{"tid":1698551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大專學界國際事務團 被陳雲點名批評","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T15:28:14.000Z","uid":299481,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"50e2a631fb4af0fe85760c383f0e2ad93fe0dc51","tid":1698551,"uid":299481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V9nNeO0yWyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV9nNeO0yWyk&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=4ead0609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V9nNeO0yWyk</a> <br />\n<br />\n好唔得wor<br />\n<br />\n大專學界國際事務團 點解在國際場合<br />\n解釋香港示威者的行為 <br />\n解釋成咁<br />\n<br />\n//理大爆料:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1219657624789220/posts/2533435660078070?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1219657624789220%2Fposts%2F2533435660078070%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=2fdc2993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1219657624789220/posts/2533435660078070?sfns=mo</a><br />\n到底HKIAD 係外國同人講左咩。<br />\n<br />\n大致上HKIAD係談話內容做了以下事項：<br />\n一）承認抗爭有領袖，而默認學生領袖為HKIAD。<br />\n二）否定勇武抗爭者 ，指出勇武不解決問題。<br />\n三）承認要起大台以操控人群。<br />\n四）目標恢復政府權威。<br />\n五）默認問題只出在香港政府。<br />\n<br />\n(理大爆料翻譯中)"},{"pid":"db74c3051a5eba6e1cb1542b7b1d4629ae9ce63c","tid":1698551,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:39:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"902bdf82309571c05df8785394fcc6aca7050a86","tid":1698551,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc6a3ba546fa0258145b88ace6d93328df6ced38","tid":1698551,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a57d43be5555fa1ecf597f3f43c7a725e025bc0","tid":1698551,"uid":181535,"like":0,"disl